{
  "stem": "5496.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In fact, Fred always teases me because, while I don't come from a religious background-- incidentally, I just must say a very comical thing.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My grandfather was a real bon vivant, and he went to a Carnival in Nice.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in those days, I mean, it was the biggest deal.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, how many people fly to Nice?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the interesting thing about it, his grandchildren, my sister, George, and me, as a gift he brought back bananas from Josephine Baker's skirt.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what I'm trying to say is that while I didn't see it by example-- although Passover was kept in my grandmother's home-- although I didn't see it so much at home, I am religious to a sense that I never gave up my belief in God.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I do light candles every Friday, and I do keep the holidays.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And whenever I can, I go to a synagogue, especially during holidays, but we don't belong to a formal synagogue as such.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And how long have you and Fred been married now?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "40 Years.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Since 1954.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Happily married.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never had.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Fred has a son from a previous marriage.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, as so many of us feel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And all I can say is that God must have had a special purpose indeed, because I was a scrawny little kid and grown men and soldiers couldn't survive, of course, the horrors and trials and tribulations.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There must have been a reason.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I always felt, and I feel my philosophy of life has become to help others.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Perhaps that's why I was in the medical field.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, in fact, I have now worked in New York and have just recently given it up.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
